"The image has <b>Exif</b> metadata and multiple layers. Only metadata <b>in "
"the first layer</b> will be saved."
msgstr ""
"Tá meiteashonraí <b>Exif</b> agus ilchiseal san íomhá. Ní shábhálfar ach "
"meiteashonraí <b>sa chéad chiseal</b>."

#: libs/impex/FillLayerTypeCheck.h:92
#, kde-format
msgctxt "image conversion warning"
