#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, gifReserveTransparent)
#: libs/ui/animation/video_export_options_dialog.ui:347
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>GIF format supports up to 256 colors per frame/image. "
"This option enables transparency at the cost of 1 color, thus only 255 "
"colors will be used for GIFs with this option enabled. Disabling this option "
"gives you the entire 256 colors for your GIF for better quality output.</"
"p><p><span style=\" font-style:italic;\">Note 1: For transparency to work "
"properly, you need to make sure that the image sequence is exporting with "
"transparency enabled, and that FFMpeg version is at least 4.2+. If your GIF "
"output shows signs of screen tearing, FFMpeg version 4.4+ is highly "
"recommended.</span></p><p><span style=\" font-style:italic;\">Note 2: GIF "
"format only supports 100% transparency, or 0% transparency. Partial "
"transparency is </span><span style=\" font-style:italic; text-decoration: "
"underline;\">not</span><span style=\" font-style:italic;\"> supported. If "
"you need partial transparency, consider APNG or WEBP.</span><br/></p></"
"body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Tacaíonn formáid GIF le suas le 256 dathanna in "
"aghaidh an fhráma/íomhá. Cumasaíonn an rogha seo trédhearcacht ar chostas 1 "
"dath, mar sin ní úsáidfear ach 255 dathanna le haghaidh GIFanna agus an "
"rogha seo cumasaithe. Má dhíchumasaíonn tú an rogha seo, gheobhaidh tú na "
"256 dathanna iomlána chun do GIF le haghaidh aschur ar chaighdeán níos fearr."
"</p><p><span style=\"font-style:italic;\">Nóta 1: Chun go n-oibreoidh "
"trédhearcacht i gceart, ní mór duit a chinntiú go bhfuil an seicheamh íomhá "
"á easpórtáil agus trédhearcacht cumasaithe, agus go bhfuil leagan FFMpeg "
"4.2+ ar a laghad. Má tá comharthaí stróicthe scáileáin le feiceáil ar aschur "
"d'GIF, moltar go mór leagan 4.4+ de FFMpeg.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-"
"style:italic;\">Nóta 2: Ní thacaíonn formáid GIF ach le 100% trédhearcachta, "
"nó 0% trédhearcachta. Ní thacaítear le trédhearcacht pháirteach.</span><span "
"style=\"font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline;\">ní</span><span "
"style=\"font-style:italic;\"> Más gá trédhearcacht pháirteach duit, "
"smaoinigh ar APNG nó WEBP.</span><br/></p></body></html>"

