#: libs/ui/dialogs/kis_about_application.cpp:132
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><h1 align=\"center\"><b>Your Rights</b></h1><p>Krita is "
"released under the GNU General Public License (version 3 or any later "
"version).</p><p>This license grants people a number of freedoms:</"
"p><ul><li>You are free to use Krita, for any purpose</li><li>You are free to "
"distribute Krita</li><li>You can study how Krita works and change it</"
"li><li>You can distribute changed versions of Krita</li></ul><p>The Krita "
"Foundation and its projects on krita.org are <b>committed</b> to preserving "
"Krita as free software.</p><h1 align=\"center\">Your artwork</h1><p>What you "
"create with Krita is your sole property. All your artwork is free for you to "
"use as you like.</p><p>That means that Krita can be used commercially, for "
"any purpose. There are no restrictions whatsoever.</p><p>Krita’s GNU GPL "
"license guarantees you this freedom. Nobody is ever permitted to take it "
"away, in contrast to trial or educational versions of commercial software "
"that will forbid your work in commercial situations.</p><br/><hr/><pre>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><h1 align=\"center\"><b>Do Chearta</b></h1><p>Scaoiltear "
"Krita faoin gCeadúnas Poiblí Ginearálta GNU (leagan 3 nó aon leagan níos "
"déanaí).</p><p>Tugann an ceadúnas seo roinnt saoirsí do dhaoine:</"
"p><ul><li>Tá tú saor chun Krita a úsáid, chun aon chríche</li><li>Tá tú saor "
"chun Krita a dháileadh</li><li>Is féidir leat staidéar a dhéanamh ar an "
"gcaoi a n-oibríonn Krita agus é a athrú</li><li>Is féidir leat leaganacha "
"athraithe de Krita a dháileadh</li></ul><p>Tá Fondúireacht Krita agus a "
"tionscadail ar krita.org <b>tiomanta</b> do Krita a chaomhnú mar bhogearraí "
"saor in aisce.</p><h1 align=\"center\">Do shaothar ealaíne</h1><p>Is leatsa "
"an t-aon mhaoin a chruthaíonn tú le Krita. Tá do shaothar ealaíne go léir "
"saor in aisce duit le húsáid mar is mian leat.</p><p>Ciallaíonn sé sin gur "
"féidir Krita a úsáid go tráchtála, chun aon chríche. Níl aon srianta ar bith "
"ann.</p><p>Ráthaíonn ceadúnas GNU GPL Krita an tsaoirse seo duit. Ní "
"cheadaítear d'aon duine é a bhaint díot riamh, i gcodarsnacht le leaganacha "
"trialach nó oideachasúla de bhogearraí tráchtála a chuirfidh cosc ar d'obair "
"i gcásanna tráchtála.</p><br/><hr/><pre>"

