#: libs/ui/dialogs/kis_dlg_preferences.cc:1310
#, kde-format
msgid "Enable canvas color management"
msgstr "Cumasaigh bainistíocht dathanna an chanbháis"

#: libs/ui/dialogs/kis_dlg_preferences.cc:1313
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Enabling canvas color management automatically creates a separate native "
"surface for the canvas. It might cause performance issues on some systems.</"
"p><p>If color management is disabled, Krita will render the canvas into the "
"surface of the main window, which is considered sRGB. It will cause two "
"limitations:<ol>    <li>the color gamut will be limited to sRGB</li>    "
"<li>color proofing mode will be limited to \"use global display settings"
"\",         i.e. paper white proofing will become impossible</li></ol></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Nuair a chumasaítear bainistíocht dathanna an chanbháis, cruthaítear "
"dromchla dúchasach ar leith don chanbhás go huathoibríoch. D’fhéadfadh sé "
"seo fadhbanna feidhmíochta a chruthú ar roinnt córas.</p><p>Má "
"dhíchumasaítear bainistíocht dathanna, déanfaidh Krita an chanbhás a "
"rindreáil i ndromchla na príomhfhuinneoige, a mheastar a bheith sRGB. "
"Cuirfidh sé seo dhá theorainn ar fáil:<ol> <li>beidh an gamut dathanna "
"teoranta do sRGB</li> <li>beidh mód cruthúnais datha teoranta do \"socruithe "
"taispeána domhanda a úsáid\", i.e. ní bheidh sé indéanta cruthúnas páipéir "
"bhán a dhéanamh</li></ol></p>"

