#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Hue hopefully maintained (but not required), lightness and saturation "
"sacrificed to maintain the perceived color. White point changed to result in "
"neutral grays. Intended for images."
msgstr ""
"Tá súil againn go gcoimeádfar an dath (ach ní gá), ach go n-íobairtear an "
"gile agus an tsáithiúlacht chun an dath a bhraitear a choinneáil. Athraítear "
"an pointe bán chun liath neodrach a chruthú. Beartaithe le haghaidh íomhánna."

