#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1138
#, kde-format
msgid "Animation Settings"
msgstr "Socruithe Beochana"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, m_chkAutoPin)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1144
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When this option is checked newly created layers will be automatically "
"pinned to the animation timeline. This is useful when animating with a small "
"number of layers or when many elements on different animated layers are "
"interacting with each other."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bheidh an rogha seo roghnaithe, déanfar sraitheanna nua-chruthaithe "
"a phionáil go huathoibríoch leis an amlíne beochana. Tá sé seo úsáideach "
"agus líon beag sraitheanna á bheochan nó nuair a bhíonn go leor eilimintí ar "
"shraitheanna beoite éagsúla ag idirghníomhú lena chéile."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, m_chkAutoPin)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1147
#, kde-format
msgid "Automatically pin new layers to timeline"
msgstr "Sraitheanna nua a phionáil go huathoibríoch leis an amlíne"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, m_chkAdaptivePlaybackRange)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1154
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When checked, this option automatically adjusts the document's \"start\" and "
"\"end\" frames so that newly created keyframes are always within the "
"animation playback range. This feature is recommended to speed up animation "
"workflow when improvising a scene without a predetermined length."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bhíonn sé seo roghnaithe, déanann an rogha seo frámaí \"tús\" agus "
"\"deireadh\" an doiciméid a choigeartú go huathoibríoch ionas go mbeidh "
"frámaí eochair nua-chruthaithe i gcónaí laistigh de raon athsheinm an "
"bheochana. Moltar an ghné seo chun sreabhadh oibre an bheochana a bhrostú "
"agus radharc á athchóiriú gan fad réamhshocraithe."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, m_chkAdaptivePlaybackRange)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1157
#, kde-format
msgid "Automatically adapt playback range to keyframes"
msgstr "Oiriúnaigh raon athsheinm go huathoibríoch do na príomhfhrámaí"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, m_chkAutoZoom)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1164
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When checked, this option will automatically scale the Animation Timeline "
"Docker's frames view to best fit the document's playback range. A smaller "
"playback range will cause the timeline to zoom in, while a larger playback "
"range will cause the timeline to zoom out."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bheidh sé roghnaithe, déanfaidh an rogha seo radharc frámaí Docker "
"Amlíne na Beochana a scálú go huathoibríoch chun go n-oirfidh sé is fearr do "
"raon athsheinm an doiciméid. Má tá raon athsheinm níos lú ann, súmálfaidh an "
"amlíne isteach, agus má tá raon athsheinm níos mó ann, súmálfaidh an amlíne "
"amach."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, m_chkAutoZoom)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1167
#, kde-format
msgid "Automatically zoom timeline to fit playback range"
msgstr "Súmáil an amlíne go huathoibríoch chun freastal ar an raon athsheinm"

