#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QLabel, label_17)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1576
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"In some Krita versions before 5.0 text size could be dependent on the "
"current display DPI (which was a bug).\n"
"In Krita 5.0 this bug has been fixed, which may cause files created in "
"previous versions look different. \n"
"\n"
"When loading old files Krita will try to adjust font size to the DPI of the "
"current screen.\n"
"If the file has been created on a different display, try adjusting this "
"value manually.\n"
"\n"
"After saving the file in Krita 5.0 at least once, no conversions will be "
"needed anymore."
msgstr ""
"I roinnt leaganacha de Krita roimh 5.0, d’fhéadfadh méid an téacs a bheith "
"ag brath ar DPI an taispeántais reatha (rud a bhí ina fhabht).\n"
"I Krita 5.0, tá an fabht seo socraithe, rud a d’fhéadfadh a bheith ina chúis "
"le cuma dhifriúil ar chomhaid a cruthaíodh i leaganacha roimhe seo.\n"
"\n"
"Nuair a bhíonn seanchomhaid á luchtú, déanfaidh Krita iarracht méid an chló "
"a choigeartú go DPI an scáileáin reatha.\n"
"Más rud é gur cruthaíodh an comhad ar thaispeántas difriúil, déan iarracht "
"an luach seo a choigeartú de láimh.\n"
"\n"
"Tar éis an comhad a shábháil i Krita 5.0 uair amháin ar a laghad, ní bheidh "
"aon chomhshó ag teastáil a thuilleadh."

