#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, chkIgnoreHighFunctionKeys)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:1730
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Some applications may emulate presses of function keys with high numbers (e."
