msgstr "Suíomh:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox_4)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:256
#, kde-format
msgid "Multithreading"
msgstr "Il-shnáitheáil"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_8)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:262
#, kde-format
msgid "CPU Limit:"
msgstr "Teorainn LAP:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (KisSliderSpinBox, sliderThreadsLimit)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:275
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Krita will not use more CPU cores than selected by "
"this limit</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Ní úsáidfidh Krita níos mó croíleacán LAP ná mar a "
"roghnaítear leis an teorainn seo</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_9)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:282
#, kde-format
msgid "Frame Rendering Clones Limit"
msgstr "Teorainn Clónanna Rindreála Frámaí"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (KisSliderSpinBox, sliderFrameClonesLimit)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:295
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>When rendering animation frames (into files or during "
"animation cache regeneration), Krita will make the specified number of "
"copies of your image and will work on them in parallel. Each copy will "
"demand more RAM for its storage (about 20% of the size of you image), so "
"raise this limit only if you have enough RAM installed.</p><p><br/></"
"p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Recommended value:</span> set Clones "
"Limit to the number of <span style=\" text-decoration: underline;"
"\">physical</span> (non-hyperthreaded) cores your CPU has</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Nuair a bhíonn frámaí beochana á rindreáil (i gcomhaid "
"nó le linn athghiniúint taisce beochana), déanfaidh Krita an líon sonraithe "
"cóipeanna de d'íomhá agus oibreoidh sé orthu go comhthreomhar. Beidh níos mó "
"RAM ag teastáil le haghaidh stórála gach cóipe (thart ar 20% de mhéid "
"d'íomhá), mar sin ná hardaigh an teorainn seo ach amháin má tá go leor RAM "
"suiteáilte agat.</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Luach "
"molta:</span> socraigh Teorainn Clónanna go dtí líon na gcroí <span style=\" "
"text-decoration: underline;\">fisiciúil</span> (neamh-hipirshnáithithe) atá "
"ag do LAP</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_11)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:302
#, kde-format
msgid "Frame Rendering Timeout"
msgstr "Am Teorann Rindreála Fráma"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (KisSliderSpinBox, sliderFrameTimeout)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:315
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>The timeout for rendering one frame. If your animation "
"rendering fails regularly with a timeout, try increasing this value</"
"p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Recommended value:</span> "
"30...60 seconds</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>An teorainn ama le haghaidh rindreáil fráma amháin. Má "
"theipeann ar rindreáil do bheochana go rialta le teorainn ama, déan iarracht "
"an luach seo a mhéadú</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-weight:600;"
"\">Luach molta:</span> 30...60 soicind</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, fpsGroup)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:325
#, kde-format
msgid "Frame rate"
msgstr "Ráta fráma"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_fps)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:331
#, kde-format
msgid "Frame rate limit:"
msgstr "Teorainn ráta fráma:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (KisSliderSpinBox, sliderFpsLimit)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:344
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Krita will try to limit the number of screen updates "
"per second to the given number. A lower number will decrease visual "
"responsiveness but increase stylus precision on some systems like macOS.<p></"
"body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Déanfaidh Krita iarracht líon na nuashonruithe "
"scáileáin in aghaidh an tsoicind a theorannú don uimhir shonraithe. "
"Laghdóidh uimhir níos ísle an fhreagrúlacht amhairc ach méadóidh sé "
"cruinneas an stíle ar roinnt córas cosúil le macOS.<p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkDetectFps)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:351
#, kde-format
msgid "Detect from screen"
msgstr "Braith ón scáileán"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox_7)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:361
#, kde-format
msgid "Debug options"
msgstr "Roghanna dífhabhtaithe"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkOpenGLFramerateLogging)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:367
#, kde-format
msgid "Debug logging of OpenGL framerate"
msgstr "Logáil dífhabhtaithe ar ráta fráma OpenGL"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkBrushSpeedLogging)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:374
#, kde-format
msgid "Debug logging for brush rendering speed"
msgstr "Logáil dífhabhtaithe le haghaidh luas rindreála scuaibe"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkDisableAVXOptimizations)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:381
#, kde-format
msgid "Disable AVX vector optimizations"
msgstr "Díchumasaigh uasmhéaduithe veicteoir AVX"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkDisableVectorOptimizations)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:388
#, kde-format
msgid "Disable all vector optimizations"
msgstr "Díchumasaigh gach uasmhéadú veicteora"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkProgressReporting)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:395
#, kde-format
msgid "Progress reporting (might affect performance)"
msgstr ""
"Tuairisciú ar dhul chun cinn (d’fhéadfadh tionchar a bheith aige ar "
"fheidhmíocht)"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkPerformanceLogging)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:402
#, kde-format
msgid "Performance logging"
msgstr "Logáil feidhmíochta"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_7)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:415
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>When performance logging is enabled Krita saves timing "
"information into the <tt>&lt;working_dir&gt;/log</tt> folder. If you "
"experience performance problems and want to help us, enable this option and "
"add the contents of the directory to a bug report.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Nuair a bhíonn logáil feidhmíochta cumasaithe, "
"sábhálann Krita faisnéis ama isteach sa bhfillteán <tt>&lt;working_dir&gt;/"
"log</tt>. Má bhíonn fadhbanna feidhmíochta agat agus más mian leat cabhrú "
"linn, cumasaigh an rogha seo agus cuir ábhar an eolaire le tuarascáil fabht."
"</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: attribute (title), widget (QWidget, AnimationCache)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:442
#, kde-format
msgid "Animation Cache"
msgstr "Taisce Beochana"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox_3)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:448
#, kde-format
msgid "Cache Storage Backend"
msgstr "Cúltaca Stórála Taisce"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QRadioButton, optInMemory)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:454
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Animation frame cache will be stored in RAM completely "
"without any limitations</p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">WARNING:</"
"span> please make sure your computer has enough RAM <span style=\" text-"
"decoration: underline;\">above</span> the amount you requested in General "
"tab. Otherwise you might face system freezes.</p><p>* for 1 second of "
"FullHD@25fps video you need extra 200 MiB of memory</p><p>* for 1 second of "
"4K UltraHD@25fps video you need extra 800 MiB of memory</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Stórálfar taisce fráma beochana i RAM gan aon "
"teorainneacha</p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">RABHADH:</span> déan "
"cinnte go bhfuil dóthain RAM ag do ríomhaire <span style=\" text-decoration: "
"underline;\">os cionn</span> an méid a d'iarr tú sa chluaisín Ginearálta. "
"Seachas sin, d'fhéadfadh go mbeadh an córas ag reo.</p><p>* le haghaidh 1 "
"soicind de fhíseán FullHD@25fps, teastaíonn 200 MiB breise cuimhne uait</"
"p><p>* le haghaidh 1 soicind de fhíseán 4K UltraHD@25fps, teastaíonn 800 MiB "
"breise cuimhne uait</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, optInMemory)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:457
#, kde-format
msgid "In-memory"
msgstr "In-chuimhne"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QRadioButton, optOnDisk)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:464
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Animation frames are stored on hard disk in the same "
"folder as swap file. The cache is stored in a compressed way. Little amount "
"of extra RAM is needed.</p><p>Since data transfer speed of the hard drive is "
"low, you might want to limit cached frame size to be able to play your video "
"at 25 fps. The limit of 2500 px is usually a good choice.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Stóráiltear frámaí beochana ar dhiosca crua san "
"fhillteán céanna leis an gcomhad malartaithe. Stóráiltear an taisce ar "
"bhealach comhbhrúite. Níl mórán RAM breise ag teastáil.</p><p>Ós rud é go "
"bhfuil luas aistrithe sonraí an tiomántáin chrua íseal, b'fhéidir gur mhaith "
"leat méid na bhfrámaí taisceáilte a theorannú chun go mbeidh tú in ann do "
"fhíseán a sheinm ag 25 fps. Is rogha mhaith de ghnáth é an teorainn de 2500 "
"px.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, optOnDisk)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:467
#, kde-format
msgid "On-disk"
msgstr "Ar dhiosca"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox_5)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:477
#, kde-format
msgid "Cache Generation Options"
msgstr "Roghanna Giniúint Taisce"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, chkCachedFramesSizeLimit)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:483
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Render scaled down version of the frame if the image "
"is bigger than the provided limit. Make sure you enable this option when "
"using on-disk storage backend.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Rindreáil leagan laghdaithe den fhráma má tá an íomhá "
"níos mó ná an teorainn atá curtha ar fáil. Cinntigh go gcumasaíonn tú an "
"rogha seo agus tú ag úsáid cúltaca stórála ar dhiosca.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkCachedFramesSizeLimit)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:486
#, kde-format
msgid "Limit cached frame size:"
msgstr "Teorainn a chur le méid fráma taisceáilte:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (KisSliderSpinBox, intCachedFramesSizeLimit)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:499
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Size limit after which the frames will be scaled down</"
"p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Recommended value:</span> 2500&nbsp;"
"px</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Teorainn méide a laghdófar na frámaí ina diaidh</"
"p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Luach molta:</span> 2500&nbsp;px</p></"
"body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, chkUseRegionOfInterest)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:506
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>When the image is too big, render only currently "
"visible part of it</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Nuair a bhíonn an íomhá ró-mhór, ní dhéantar ach cuid "
"di atá le feiceáil faoi láthair a rindreáil</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkUseRegionOfInterest)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:509
#, kde-format
msgid "Use region of interest"
msgstr "Úsáid réigiún spéise"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (KisSliderSpinBox, intRegionOfInterestMargin)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:522
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Add extra area to the region of interest to each side "
"of the canvas.</p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Recommended value:</"
"span> 25%. The region of interest will be extended by 25% to each side.</p></"
"body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Cuir achar breise leis an réigiún spéise ar gach taobh "
"den chanbhás.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Luach molta:</span> "
"25%. Leathnófar an réigiún spéise faoi 25% ar gach taobh.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, chkBackgroundCacheGeneration)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:529
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Automatically prerender animation cache in background "
"when the user is idle</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Rinne taisce beochana go huathoibríoch sa chúlra nuair "
"a bhíonn an t-úsáideoir díomhaoin</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkBackgroundCacheGeneration)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:532
#, kde-format
msgid "Enable background cache generation"
msgstr "Cumasaigh giniúint taisce cúlra"

#. i18n: ectx: attribute (title), widget (QWidget, InstantPreview)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:556
#: libs/ui/widgets/kis_lod_availability_widget.cpp:168
#, kde-format
msgid "Instant Preview"
msgstr "Réamhamharc Meandarach"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkTransformToolUseInStackPreview)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:565
#, kde-format
msgid "Use in-stack preview in Transform Tool"
msgstr "Úsáid réamhamharc in-stack in Transform Tool"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox_6)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:572
#, kde-format
msgid "Force Instant Preview"
msgstr "Fórsaigh Réamhamharc Meandarach"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, chkFiltersForceLodMode)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:578
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>The filter dialog will always use instant preview, "
"even if instant preview is disabled in the &quot;View&quot; menu</p></body></"
"html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Úsáidfidh an dialóg scagaire réamhamharc láithreach i "
"gcónaí, fiú má tá réamhamharc láithreach díchumasaithe sa roghchlár &quot;"
"Amharc&quot;</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkFiltersForceLodMode)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:581
#, kde-format
msgid "in Filters"
msgstr "i Scagairí"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, chkTransformToolForceLodMode)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:588
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>The transform tool preview will always use instant "
"preview, even if instant preview is disabled in the &quot;View&quot; menu</"
"p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Úsáidfidh réamhamharc an uirlis chlaochlaithe "
"réamhamharc meandarach i gcónaí, fiú má tá réamhamharc meandarach "
"díchumasaithe sa roghchlár &quot;Amharc&quot;</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkTransformToolForceLodMode)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:591
#, kde-format
msgid "in Transform Tool"
msgstr "san Uirlis Claochlaithe"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, chkMoveToolForceLodMode)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:598
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>The move tool preview will always use instant preview, "
"even if instant preview is disabled in the &quot;View&quot; menu</p></body></"
"html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Úsáidfidh réamhamharc an uirlis bhogtha réamhamharc "
"meandarach i gcónaí, fiú má tá réamhamharc meandarach díchumasaithe sa "
"roghchlár &quot;Amharc&quot;</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, chkMoveToolForceLodMode)
#: libs/ui/forms/wdgperformancesettings.ui:601
#, kde-format
msgid "in Move Tool"
msgstr "san Uirlis Bogtha"

