#, kde-format
msgctxt "@tooltip"
msgid ""
"Greater value will produce a larger file and a better quality. Doesn't "
"affect CPU consumption.\n"
"Values lower than 50 are not recommended due to high artifacts."
msgstr ""
"Má tá luach níos mó agat, beidh comhad níos mó agus caighdeán níos fearr "
"agat. Ní dhéanann sé difear do thomhaltas an LAP.\n"
"Ní mholtar luachanna níos ísle ná 50 mar gheall ar líon ard artifachtanna."

