#: plugins/dockers/textproperties/qml/DominantBaseline.qml:16
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Dominant baseline specifies how stretches of text of different sizes are "
"aligned, it is also the default for Alignment Baseline."
msgstr ""
"Sonraíonn an bunlíne cheannasach conas a ailínítear píosaí téacs de "
"mhéideanna difriúla, agus is é an réamhshocrú é freisin do Bhunlíne "
"Ailínithe."

