msgstr "Uath"

#: plugins/dockers/textproperties/qml/DominantBaseline.qml:81
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Aligns to alphabetic baseline when laying out horizontally, aligns to "
"central baseline when laying out vertically."
msgstr ""
"Ailíníonn sé leis an mbonnlíne aibítreach agus é á leagan amach go "
"cothrománach, ailíníonn sé leis an mbonnlíne lárnach agus é á leagan amach "
"go hingearach."

#: plugins/dockers/textproperties/qml/FontFamily.qml:14
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Font Family"
msgstr "Teaghlach Clónna"

#: plugins/dockers/textproperties/qml/FontFamily.qml:19
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Font family allows selecting a list of fonts that should be used for the "
"current text. The first font family is the primary font used, while each "
"font family after that is used for fallback."
msgstr ""
"Leis an teaghlach clónna, is féidir liosta clónna a roghnú ar cheart iad a "
"úsáid don téacs reatha. Is é an chéad teaghlach clónna an príomhchló a "
"úsáidtear, agus úsáidtear gach teaghlach cló ina dhiaidh sin mar chúltaca."

#: plugins/dockers/textproperties/qml/FontFamily.qml:21
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"comma separated search terms for the font-family property, matching is case-"
"insensitive"
msgid "font-family, typeface, font, fallback"
msgstr "cló-chló, cló-aghaidh, cló, rogha eile"

#: plugins/dockers/textproperties/qml/FontFamily.qml:149
#, kde-format
