#: plugins/impex/exr/exr_converter.cc:920
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"The image contains pixels with zero alpha channel and non-zero color "
"channels. Krita has modified those pixels to have at least some alpha. The "
"initial values will <i>not</i> be reverted on saving the image back.<br/><br/"
">This will hardly make any visual difference just keep it in mind."
msgstr ""
"Tá picteilíní san íomhá le cainéal alfa nialasach agus bealaí datha neamh-"
"nialasacha. Tá na picteilíní sin modhnaithe ag Krita chun roinnt alfa a "
"bheith acu ar a laghad. <i>Ní</i> aisiompófar na luachanna tosaigh nuair a "
"shábhálfar an íomhá ar ais.<br/><br/>Is ar éigean a dhéanfaidh sé seo aon "
"difríocht amhairc ach coinnigh i gcuimhne é."

#: plugins/impex/exr/exr_converter.cc:927
