"artifacts get introduced. <br/>Note: A quality of 100 switches to lossless "
"compression similar to (but often more efficient than) PNG.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Coigeartaigh cáilíocht na híomhá. Dá ísle an cháilíocht, is ea is mó de "
"na déantáin chomhbhrúite a chuirtear isteach. <br/>Nóta: Athraíonn cáilíocht "
"100 go comhbhrú gan chailliúint cosúil le (ach is minic a bhíonn sé níos "
"éifeachtaí ná) PNG.</p>"

#: plugins/impex/raw/3rdparty/libkdcraw/src/dcrawsettingswidget.cpp:263
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "16 bits color depth"
msgstr "Doimhneacht datha 16 giotán"

#: plugins/impex/raw/3rdparty/libkdcraw/src/dcrawsettingswidget.cpp:264
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<p>If enabled, all RAW files will be decoded in 16-bit color depth using a "
"linear gamma curve. To prevent dark picture rendering in the editor, it is "
"recommended to use Color Management in this mode.</p><p>If disabled, all RAW "
"files will be decoded in 8-bit color depth with a BT.709 gamma curve and a "
"99th-percentile white point. This mode is faster than 16-bit decoding.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar gach comhad RAW a dhíchódú i ndoimhneacht "
"datha 16-giotán ag baint úsáide as cuar gáma líneach. Chun rindreáil pictiúr "
"dorcha san eagarthóir a chosc, moltar Bainistíocht Datha a úsáid sa mhodh "
"seo.</p><p>Má tá sé díchumasaithe, déanfar gach comhad RAW a dhíchódú i "
"ndoimhneacht datha 8-giotán le cuar gáma BT.709 agus pointe bán 99ú "
"peircintíl. Tá an modh seo níos tapúla ná díchódú 16-giotán.</p>"

#: plugins/impex/raw/3rdparty/libkdcraw/src/dcrawsettingswidget.cpp:283
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Interpolate RGB as four colors"
msgstr "Idirshuigh RGB mar cheithre dhath"

#: plugins/impex/raw/3rdparty/libkdcraw/src/dcrawsettingswidget.cpp:284
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Interpolate RGB as four colors</title><p>The default is to assume "
"that all green pixels are the same. If even-row green pixels are more "
"sensitive to ultraviolet light than odd-row this difference causes a mesh "
"pattern in the output; using this option solves this problem with minimal "
"loss of detail.</p><p>To resume, this option blurs the image a little, but "
"it eliminates false 2x2 mesh patterns with VNG quality method or mazes with "
"AHD quality method.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Idirshuigh RGB mar cheithre dhath</title><p>Is é an réamhshocrú ná "
"glacadh leis go bhfuil na picteilíní glasa uile mar an gcéanna. Má tá "
"picteilíní glasa i sraitheanna cothroma níos íogaire do sholas ultraivialait "
"ná picteilíní i sraitheanna corra, cruthaíonn an difríocht seo patrún "
"mogaill san aschur; réitíonn an rogha seo an fhadhb seo le cailliúint íosta "
"sonraí.</p><p>Chun atosú, déanann an rogha seo an íomhá a doiléiriú beagán, "
"ach cuireann sé deireadh le patrúin mogaill bhréagacha 2x2 le modh "
"cáilíochta VNG nó le modh cáilíochta AHD.</p>"

#: plugins/impex/raw/3rdparty/libkdcraw/src/dcrawsettingswidget.cpp:298
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Visit LibRaw project website"
msgstr "Tabhair cuairt ar shuíomh gréasáin thionscadail LibRaw"

#: plugins/impex/raw/3rdparty/libkdcraw/src/dcrawsettingswidget.cpp:308
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Do not stretch or rotate pixels"
msgstr "Ná síneadh ná rothlú picteilíní"

#: plugins/impex/raw/3rdparty/libkdcraw/src/dcrawsettingswidget.cpp:310
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Do not stretch or rotate pixels</title><p>For Fuji Super CCD cameras, "
"show the image tilted 45 degrees. For cameras with non-square pixels, do not "
"stretch the image to its correct aspect ratio. In any case, this option "
"guarantees that each output pixel corresponds to one RAW pixel.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Ná sín ná rothlaigh picteilíní</title><p>I gcás ceamaraí Fuji Super "
"CCD, taispeáin an íomhá claonta 45 céim. I gcás ceamaraí le picteilíní "
"neamhchearnógacha, ná sín an íomhá go dtí a cóimheas gné ceart. Ar aon nós, "
"ráthaíonn an rogha seo go gcomhfhreagraíonn gach picteilín aschuir do "
"phicteilín RAW amháin.</p>"

