"When in non-buildup mode, shows how fast the deformation limit is reached."
msgstr ""
"Nuair nach bhfuil sé i mód tógála, taispeánann sé cé chomh tapa agus a "
"shroichtear an teorainn dífhoirmithe."

#: plugins/tools/tool_transform2/kis_tool_transform_config_widget.cpp:237
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Switch between Build Up and Wash mode of painting. Build Up mode adds "
"deformations one on top of the other without any limits. Wash mode gradually "
"deforms the piece to the selected deformation level."
msgstr ""
"Athraigh idir mód Tógála Suas agus Nigh na péintéireachta. Cuireann mód "
"Tógála Suas dífhoirmíochtaí ceann ar bharr an chinn eile gan aon "
"teorainneacha. Déanann mód Nigh an píosa a dhífhoirmiú de réir a chéile go "
"dtí an leibhéal dífhoirmíochta roghnaithe."

